OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy firms call for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwindfall tax to fall with  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fprices                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy firms have called on ministers  
OL,6, to reduce the windfall tax as oil and  
OL,7, gas prices fall, ahead of a package of 
OL,8, measures on energy security expected to
OL,9, be announced on Thursday.              
OL,11,FTrade body Offshore Energies UK said   
OL,12,Fthat "when prices drop, it is fair that
OL,13,Fthe windfall tax should fall away".    
OL,15,FIt came as the Financial Times reported
OL,16,Fthat ministers are set to offer energy 
OL,17,Ffirms relief on windfall taxes.        
OL,19,FThe Treasury insists it keeps all taxes
OL,20,Funder review.                          
